            "id": 6167483,
            "title": "《異動股》京東集團升近6%突破250天線,現報140.4元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社25日專訊》京東集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09618:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09618\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09618-HK</a>)現升近6%,最高價見140.4元,較ADR收市高出3.7%,創1個月新高,升穿250天線(139.224元),最低價134.4元;成交1137萬股,成交金額15.54億元;主動買沽比率64:36,資金淨主動買入4.12億元。現時最大淨被動買入券商為瑞銀,金額5243萬元,加權平均成交價136.712元;現時最大淨被動賣出券商為ABN　AMRO　CLEARING　HK,金額8356萬元,加權平均成交價136.577元。以現價計,該股暫連升2日,累計升幅9.4%。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　另外,其<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>櫃台股份(89618-HK)升5.8%,報128.6元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>,最高價128元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>,最低價123元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>;成交2.63萬股,成交金額330.58萬<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　現時,恒生指數報26558,升39點或0.1%;恒生中國企業指數報9466,升23點或0.3%;恒生科技指數報6408,升85點或1.4%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　基本資料</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　====</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>現價</td><td>140.400</td><td>變動</td><td>+5.56%</td></tr><tr><td>最高價</td><td>140.400</td><td>最低價</td><td>134.400</td></tr><tr><td>成交股數</td><td>1137萬股</td><td>成交金額</td><td>15.54億</td></tr><tr><td>10天平均</td><td>133.910</td><td>歷史波幅%</td><td>45.421</td></tr><tr><td>20天平均</td><td>128.665</td><td>加權平均價</td><td>136.616</td></tr><tr><td>50天平均</td><td>126.584</td><td>RSI14</td><td>62.367</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">股份狀態:創1個月新高,升穿250天線;主動買沽比率64:36,資金淨主動買入4.12億元;暫連升2日,累計升幅9.4%</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　表列同板塊或相關股份表現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　============</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>股份(編號)</td><td>現價(元)</td><td>變幅(%)</td></tr><tr><td>京東集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09618:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09618\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09618-HK</a>)</td><td>140.40</td><td>+5.56</td></tr><tr><td>騰訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00700:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00700\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00700-HK</a>)</td><td>656.00</td><td>+1.16</td></tr><tr><td>快手(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01024:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01024\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01024-HK</a>)</td><td>78.45</td><td>+2.08</td></tr><tr><td>小米(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01810:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01810\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01810-HK</a>)</td><td>57.85</td><td>+1.67</td></tr><tr><td>美團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03690:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03690\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03690-HK</a>)</td><td>101.90</td><td>-0.29</td></tr><tr><td>嗶哩嗶哩(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09626:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09626\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09626-HK</a>)</td><td>216.00</td><td>+4.65</td></tr><tr><td>小鵬汽車(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09868:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09868\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09868-HK</a>)</td><td>85.00</td><td>+2.04</td></tr><tr><td>百度(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09888:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09888\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09888-HK</a>)</td><td>135.20</td><td>+5.13</td></tr><tr><td>阿里(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09988:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09988\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09988-HK</a>)</td><td>175.30</td><td>+0.75</td></tr><tr><td>京東集團-SWR(89618-HK)</td><td>128.50人幣</td><td>+5.67</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(ed)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
